---
// src/components/sections/Hero.astro
---

<section id="hero" class="relative w-full pt-32 pb-24 md:pt-40 md:pb-32 border-t border-[var(--ds-border)] mt-20">
  <div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-6 md:px-8">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-start text-left max-w-4xl">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-[0.15em] text-[var(--ds-accent)] uppercase mb-6 ds-reveal">
        DESARROLLO DE SOFTWARE A MEDIDA
      </p>

      <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-[var(--ds-text)] sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[4.2rem] leading-[1.1] ds-reveal">
        Deja de perder tiempo y dinero en operaciones manuales.
      </h1>

      <p class="mt-8 text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-[var(--ds-muted)] max-w-2xl ds-reveal">
        Elimina los cuellos de botella y errores humanos que frenan tu crecimiento. Desarrollamos sistemas de gestión que automatizan tus procesos, reducen costos operativos y escalan tus ganancias.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4 text-sm font-medium text-[var(--ds-text)] ds-reveal">
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--ds-accent)]">✓</span> Reduce costos operativos</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--ds-accent)]">✓</span> Ahorra cientos de horas</span>
        <span class="flex items-center gap-2"><span class="text-[var(--ds-accent)]">✓</span> Control en tiempo real</span>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col items-start gap-6 w-full sm:flex-row sm:items-center ds-reveal">
        <a href="#diagnostico" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--ds-accent)] bg-[var(--ds-text)] px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-black transition-colors hover:bg-[var(--ds-accent)] hover:text-black w-full sm:w-auto">
          Solicitar diagnóstico operativo
        </a>
        <a href="#casos" class="text-base font-medium text-[var(--ds-text)] hover:text-[var(--ds-accent)] transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1 w-full sm:w-auto justify-center sm:justify-start">
          Ver casos reales <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="mt-10 text-sm text-[var(--ds-muted)] ds-reveal">
        Sin contratos de permanencia · Diagnóstico inicial sin costo
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>